    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Vanos system has been fully overhauled for precise variable valve timing, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the iconic handling characteristics of this longitudinal RWD masterpiece. A turn-key, mechanically flawless example for the serious enthusiast.",
